  "description": "Per-service board for the NetBird unified management + signal server (job=\"netbird-server\", scraped at 172.17.0.2:9090). Metric names taken verbatim from the live /metrics endpoint: the OTel Prometheus exporter appends unit suffixes to instrument names that already carry the unit (e.g. *_duration_ms_milliseconds, connected_streams_ratio, *_micro_microseconds). No peer/account totals are exposed (those go to PostHog, not /metrics). Datasource is the fixed provisioned uid \"victoriametrics\".",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
